<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (trtạḥ ạlnfws.. wttʿlm drws.. fy mḥḍr ạlqdws
 yrtạḥ ạlḍmyr .. wytmly btạ̉tẖyr .. ạ̉ʿẓm ḥb wtqdyr)2
 ạlqrạr-(jlsẗ tnsynạ ậlạm .. wjrạḥ whmwm ạlywm)2
 (jlsẗ btdynạ slạm .. yfḍl wyạnạ wydwm)2
 2- (trtạḥ ạlqlwb .. ttạ̉tẖr wttwb .. qdạm ạ̹lh mṣlwb
 ttmly ạlạ̉fwạh .. bạlsẖkr wạlṣlạẗ .. lly ạ̹dạnạ ạlḥyạẗ)2
 3- (ttsẖạl ạlhmwm wtzwl ạlgẖywm .. wyḥl frḥ wydwm
 tnthy ạlậlạm wyfyḍ ạlslạm .. fy ạlqlb bṭwl ạlywm)2</lyrics>
<title>trtạḥ ạlnfws</title>
</song>